# Agent Playbooks

When the user asks for role-specific support, load the matching playbook:

- `agents/sre-agent.md` - incident response, operations, and reliability.
- `agents/testing-agent.md` - risk-based test strategy and validation.
- `agents/code-review-agent.md` - severity-first review focused on bugs and risk.

Cursor skill wrappers are also available under `.cursor/skills/`.

